Output assets/cmdpeek-search-demo.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1800
Set Height 800
Set TypingSpeed 60ms
Set Theme "Dracula"

Require cmdpeek

Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "cmdpeek"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "/"
Sleep 700ms

Type "example"
Sleep 1.5s

Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "123"
Sleep 800ms
Enter
Sleep 2s

Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "y"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 3s
